## Code Review Checklist

### General
- [ ] Code follows project style guidelines
- [ ] All tests pass and coverage is maintained
- [ ] Documentation is updated for new features
- [ ] Security considerations are addressed
- [ ] Performance impact is considered

### Backend (Django)
- [ ] Models include proper validation and constraints
- [ ] Views implement proper permission checks
- [ ] API endpoints follow RESTful conventions
- [ ] Database migrations are backwards compatible
- [ ] Error handling is comprehensive

### Frontend (React)
- [ ] Components are properly structured and reusable
- [ ] State management is appropriate for the use case
- [ ] Accessibility requirements are met
- [ ] Performance optimizations are implemented
- [ ] Responsive design is properly implemented